  ──────────── ──────── ────────────────────
  TRD-011      INTC              $  3,010.00

[MISSING IN LEDGER]  (1 found)
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  Trade ID      Bank Amount Settled
  ──────────── ────────────────────
  TRD-020               $    500.00

────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  SUMMARY
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  Amount mismatches      : 2
  Missing in bank        : 1
  Missing in ledger      : 1
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
```

### Findings Breakdown

| Issue | Trade | Detail |
|---|---|---|
| Amount Mismatch | TRD-002 (TSLA) | Ledger expects $3,510.00 (5 × $700 + $10 fee). Bank settled $3,500.00. **Delta: -$10.00** — fee likely not included by bank. |
| Amount Mismatch | TRD-014 (SHOP) | Ledger expects $560.00 (10 × $55 + $10 fee). Bank settled $500.00. **Delta: -$60.00** — fee excluded and possible price discrepancy. |
| Missing in Bank | TRD-011 (INTC) | Ledger shows a $3,010.00 trade. No corresponding bank settlement record exists. |
| Missing in Ledger | TRD-020 | Bank has a $500.00 settlement entry with no matching internal ledger record — potential ghost trade. |
